headline: Wells Fargo serves as presenting sponsor for 2025 Thurgood Marshall College Fund Leadership Institute
summary: Washington, D.C., Sept. 30, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Wells Fargo serves as presenting sponsor for 2025 Thurgood Marshall College Fund Leadership InstituteWells Fargo proudly continues its enduring support as presenting sponsor of the Thurgood Marshall College Fund’s (TMCF) Leadership Institute, the organization’s signature professional development program serving students attending historically Black colleges and universities (HBCUs).
